trans-unit.source: JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter merges navigation back history and navigation forward history (as exposed by <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"></xref> or <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow"></xref>) into a single, [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-style navigation menu.
trans-unit.target: JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter sammanfogar tillbaka historik och historik för navigering framåt (som exponeras av <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow"> </xref>) till en enda [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-format för navigering.

trans-unit.source: Both <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> and <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> display navigation chrome that supports history navigation using the following mechanisms: - A button for navigating back one piece of content at a time.
trans-unit.target: Både <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>och <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>Visa navigering chrome som stöder historik navigering med hjälp av följande metoder:-en knapp för att navigera tillbaka en del av innehåll i taget.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>

trans-unit.source: - A button for navigating forward one piece of content at a time.
trans-unit.target: -En knapp för navigering framåt en del av innehåll i taget.

trans-unit.source: - An [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-style drop-down list that shows: - A combined list of up to nine items in back navigation history and up to nine items in forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: -En [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-style listrutan som visar:-en kombinerad lista med upp till nio objekt i tillbaka historik och upp till nio objekt i historiken för navigering framåt.

trans-unit.source: - The position of the current piece of content with respect to both back and forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: -Positionen för den aktuella typ av innehåll med avseende på både tillbaka och historik för navigering framåt.

trans-unit.source: The navigation history is stored by both <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> in the following properties: **Back Navigation History**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Historiken lagras av både <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>och <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>i följande egenskaper: **tillbaka historik**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: **Forward Navigation History**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: **Vidarebefordra historik**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: To create the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-style drop-down list, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> use JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter to merge their individual back navigation history and forward navigation history into a single list of navigation history entries.
trans-unit.target: Att skapa den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-style nedrullningsbara listan <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>och <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>använder JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter slå samman deras enskilda tillbaka historik och vidarebefordra historik till en lista av navigeringen historikposter.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: The resulting list contains up to nine entries from back navigation history and up to nine entries from forward navigation history, plus an entry for the current content.
trans-unit.target: Listan innehåller upp till nio poster från den bakre historik och upp till nio poster från historiken för navigering framåt, plus en post för det aktuella innehållet.

trans-unit.source: If you create custom navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], and need to provide an [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-style drop-down list, you can use JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter to similar effect.
trans-unit.target: Om du skapar anpassade navigering [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], och du måste ange en [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-style listrutan, kan du använda JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter att liknande effekt.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Merges two navigation history stacks.
trans-unit.target: Sammanfogar två navigering historik stackar.

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, the navigation stacks are available from the following properties: - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A> For <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, the navigation stacks are available from the following properties: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A> <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A> The two passed navigation stacks are combined into a single navigation stack that contains up to nine items from each navigation stack plus the current item.
trans-unit.target: För <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, navigering stackar är tillgängliga från följande egenskaper:- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A>för <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, navigering stackar är tillgängliga från följande egenskaper:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A><xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A>två skickade navigering stackar kombineras till en enda navigeringsstack som innehåller upp till nio artiklar från stacken varje navigering och det aktuella objektet.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>
